---
title: Smart Beef Crunch Salad with Peanuts and Edamame
description: Crunchy coleslaw mix and crisp sweet bell peppers add fun to every bite of this salad. Soy and mirin combine in a sweet, sticky glaze that dresses ground beef and protein-rich edamame.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salade-croquante-au-boeuf-524b0103.jpg
